Share a Lightning Report or Dashboard Folder

To share a report or dashboard folder, open the folders list on the Analytics, Reports, or Dashboards tab. Click Share, select who to share with from the dropdown menu, choose an access level, and click Share.

The Analytics tab doesnâ€™t support sharing with partner roles. To delete a Who Can Access entry, click X next to it.

Required Editions and User Permissions:

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Needed:

To share report folders: Manage Reports in Public Folders
To share dashboard folders: Manage Dashboards in Public Folders
title: Sharing Lightning Report or Dashboard Folder in Salesforce
